data.description: WATERFRONT priced right! Peace and serenity await with this quaint, well-kept 3 bed/2 full bath home w/ NEW ROOF just 5 minutes to downtown DeFuniak Springs. This light-filled home includes tile floors throughout, except the bedrooms which have brand new carpet. The u-shaped kitchen has ample counter space, a pantry and an oversized utility room with a brand new water heater. The renovated master bath includes tub & tile surround, new vanity and fixtures and a walk in closet in master bedroom. The real treat is the view to the lake - which you have from the living room, kitchen, master suite AND back patio!  If you love to fish or just want to sit on the patio and look out over the scenic lake, then you will love this home
